---
// src/components/Testimonials.astro
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components'
---
<section id="testimoni" class="py-20 md:py-24 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">
        Dipercaya oleh <span class="text-blue-600">Ratusan Kreator & Bisnis</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Jangan hanya dengarkan dari kami. Lihat bagaimana optimasi interaksi membantu mereka tampil lebih meyakinkan di dunia digital.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      
      <div class="animate-on-scroll-testi opacity-0 translate-y-12 transform transition-all duration-700 ease-out bg-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg relative">
        <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 text-slate-100">
          <Icon name="lucide:quote" class="w-10 h-10" />
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-1 text-amber-400 mb-5 relative z-10">
          <Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 italic relative z-10">
          "Awalnya iseng nyoba pancing like di konten baru, ternyata ngaruh banget ke algoritma. Video TikTok saya jadi dapet dorongan views yang bagus dan akhirnya bisa tembus FYP secara organik!"
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 relative z-10">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm">R</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm md:text-base font-bold text-slate-900">Rizky A.</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Content Creator</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll-testi opacity-0 translate-y-12 transform transition-all duration-700 ease-out delay-150 bg-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg relative">
        <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 text-slate-100">
          <Icon name="lucide:quote" class="w-10 h-10" />
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-1 text-amber-400 mb-5 relative z-10">
          <Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 italic relative z-10">
          "Sangat membantu buat naikin social proof toko online baru saya di IG. Konsumen yang mampir jadi nggak ragu lagi buat beli karena interaksi di tiap postingan produk kelihatan hidup."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 relative z-10">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm">S</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm md:text-base font-bold text-slate-900">Siska M.</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Owner Online Shop</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll-testi opacity-0 translate-y-12 transform transition-all duration-700 ease-out delay-300 bg-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg relative">
        <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 text-slate-100">
          <Icon name="lucide:quote" class="w-10 h-10" />
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-1 text-amber-400 mb-5 relative z-10">
          <Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 italic relative z-10">
          "Paling suka karena layanannya murni cuma minta link tautan aja, tanpa ribet minta password akun atau data sensitif lainnya. Privasi aman, pengerjaannya juga rapi dan polanya natural."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 relative z-10">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm">D</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm md:text-base font-bold text-slate-900">Dimas P.</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Digital Marketer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.addEventListener("astro:page-load", () => {
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.remove('opacity-0', 'translate-y-12');
          entry.target.classList.add('opacity-100', 'translate-y-0');
          observer.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.1 });

    const boxes = document.querySelectorAll('.animate-on-scroll-testi');
    boxes.forEach((box) => observer.observe(box));
  });
</script>

